/*******
Design a program that dispalys the following information
#1
- Your name
- Your address, with city, state, and Zip
- Your telphone number
- your college Major 

/****
Pseudoe Code:
Start
Declare name string
Declare address integer 
Declare city string 
Declare state string 
Declare zip string
Declare telephoneNum integer 
Declare collegeMaj string

Display "What is your name: " 
input name  
Display "What is your address: " 
input address
Display "what is your city: " 
input city 
Display "what is your state: "
input state 
Declare "what is your zip code: " 
input zip 
Declare "what is your Telephone number: " 
input telephoneNum
Declare "what is your college major: "
input collegeMaj 
Display "Your Name: address: city: state: zip: telephone number: college Major: ", name & address & city & state & zip & telephoneNum & collegeMaj
*******/

